The '''Unofficial PZ Animation Discord''' is a community-driven Discord server dedicated to cinematic animations, often refered to as [[Rendering|renders]] made in [[wikipedia:Blender|Blender]].

== See also ==
*[[Unofficial Mapping Discord]] – a more suitable place to discuss about [[mapping]].
*[[PZ Modding Community]] - a Discord to discuss programming and asset making to make mods.

